<https://w3id.org/EVI> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The Evidence Graph ontology extends core concepts from the W3C Provenance Ontology PROV-O and Bioschemas' Profiles to describe evidence for correctness of findings in biomedical publications. The semantic data model in EVI is expressed using OWL2 Web Ontology Language (OWL2)."@en .
